        "start": 13,
        "end": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000006",
    "sentence": "檀對曰：「方今外戚豪盛，陽道微弱，斯豈嘉瑞乎？」祗乃止。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000007",
    "sentence": "永寧元年 ，南昌有婦人生四子，祗復問檀變異之應。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000008",
    "sentence": "檀以爲京師當有兵氣，其禍發於蕭墻。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000009",
    "sentence": "至 延光四年 ，中黃門孫程揚兵殿省，誅皇後兄車騎將軍閻顯等，立濟陰王爲天子，果如所占。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "四年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000010",
    "sentence": "永建五年 ，舉孝廉，除郎中。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "五年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000011",
    "sentence": "是時白虹貫日，檀因上便宜三事，陳其咎徵。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000012",
    "sentence": "書奏，棄官去。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000013",
    "sentence": "著書二十八篇，名爲《唐子》。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "《唐子》",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 13
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000014",
    "sentence": "卒於家。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000015",
    "sentence": "公沙穆",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000016",
    "sentence": "公沙穆字文乂，北海膠東人也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000017",
    "sentence": "家貧賤，自爲兒童不好戲弄，長習《 韓詩 》、《 公羊春秋 》，尤鋭思《河》、《洛》推步之術。",
    "entities": [
      {
