  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000044",
    "sentence": "其餘多此類云。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000045",
    "sentence": "趙彥",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000046",
    "sentence": "趙彥者，琅邪人也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000047",
    "sentence": "少有術學。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_082c_000048",
    "sentence": "延熹三年 ，琅邪賊勞丙與太山賊叔孫無忌殺都尉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "三年",
